OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening to come then feeling chilly
OL,7,Funder clear skies. Soon turning
OL,8,Fcloudier again with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fand a freshening breeze. Remaining
OL,10,Fgenerally frost-free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Fand drizzle, most persistent through
OL,14,Fthe morning and turning heavy at times
OL,15,Fover the hills. Perhaps some drier
OL,16,Fspells in the afternoon. Breezy and
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
